First thing to do is to have a PC, a cable, Virtual desktop, Virtual desktop streamer, Steam VR, Gorilla Tag and Monke mod manager.
Now first download monke mod manager - https://github.com/DeadlyKitten/MonkeModManager/releases/tag/1.3.0 and download eyerock mods - 
https://bit.lyEyeRocksDarkModMenu now go into monke mod manager and select all the mods you want and click install/update and then
load up Virtual desktop and make sure to follow the instructions to conenct it to your PC now load up Steam VR and once your'e in
load into Gorilla Tag and use the mods, but if you use them in public lobbies you may get banned for up to four weeks use the mod menu
at your own risk.
